{"type":"answer","id":15967,"parentType":"question","parentId":3243,"uid":1416,"contents":"<b>(I)</b><br>\n设帮扶负责人连续四天到杨老汉家走访的事件为A，则：<br>\nP(A) = (1/2)^4 = 1/16 = 0.0625<br>\n<br>\n<b>(II)</b><br>\n由题易知，X可取0、1、2、3或4,其中：<br>\nP(X = 0) = (1 - 1/4) * (1 - 1/3) * (1 - 1/2) = 1/4<br>\nP(X = 1) = 1/4 * (1 - 1/3) * (1 - 1/2) + (1 - 1/4) * 1/3 * (1 - 1/2) + (1 - 1/4) * (1 - 1/3) * 1/2 = 11/24<br>\nP(X = 2) = 1/4 * 1/3 * (1 - 1/2) + 1/4 * (1 - 1/3) * 1/2 + (1 - 1/4) * 1/3 * 1/2 = 1/4<br>\nP(X = 3) = 1/4 * 1/3 * 1/2 = 1/24<br>\n∴ X的分布列如下图所示：<br>\n| X | 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 |<br>\n| P(X) | 1/4 | 11/24 | 1/4 | 1/24 |<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>(III)</b><br>\nE(X) = 0 * 1/4 + 1 * 11/24 +2 * 1/4 + 1/24 = 0 + 11/24 + 12/24&nbsp; + 1/24 = 1 &gt;= 1<br>\n∴ 张老汉说的是<s>真的</s>。","date":"2019-04-06","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":1}